com.centurylink.mdw.dataaccess.file

Class RuntimeDataAccessVcs

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.centurylink.mdw.dataaccess.db.CommonDataAccess
      • com.centurylink.mdw.dataaccess.file.RuntimeDataAccessVcs
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RuntimeDataAccess

    public class RuntimeDataAccessVcs
extends CommonDataAccess
implements RuntimeDataAccess
    Used for VCS-based assets in the runtime container (not Designer). Accesses the db, but takes into account the fact that the design-time tables don't exist. Also handles compatibility for pre-VCS processes that still reside in the db.
